quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  14,34,"Ne nabahelesia mubuli shiamumusaba. Ne nimubala emikabo chia Nyasaye, shimunyala okhuchimala tawe. Toto Omundu ni owamabii omukhongo, owubula okhupa orio tawe."
  14,35,"Ne olwa Ibrahim yaboola mbu; “Nyasaye wanje Omulesi, khola litokho lino libe nomulembe, ne unde ehale esie nende abana banje nende likhuwa lia okhulaama ebifwanani."
  14,36,"Nyasaye wanje Omulesi, toto (ebifwanani) ebio biakosia abandu abanji. Kho, ulonda esie, oyo niye owanje. Naye ukhaya, toto ewe oli omunji wobulesheli, omunji wetsimbabaasi."
  14,37,"Nyasaye wefu Omulesi, toto esie emenyiyie abandu banje bandi mulitwoma libulamwo omumela tawe, ahambi nende inzu yiyo yoluyali; Nyasaye wefu Omulesi, khobalaame khatsoso (Iswala). Kho, khola emioyo chiabandu chibechomekhwo, ne obahelesie emikabo chiebiamo, kho banyoole okhupa orio."
  14,38,"Nyasaye wefu Omulesi, toto ewe omanyile kakhufisanga nende akakhuretsanga habulafu. Ne shibulaho shiosishiosi shiifisanga khu Nyasaye, khushialo nohomba mwikulu tawe."
  14,39,"Okhwitsomibwa nikhwa Nyasaye, owambelesia nengofule Ismail nende Is-haq. Toto Nyasaye wanje Omulesi ni Omuwulili muno wamasayo."
  14,40,"Nyasaye wanje Omulesi, khola embe wokhulaama khatsotso Iswala, nende olwibulo lwanje. Nyasaye wefu Omulesi, fuchililila amasayo."
  14,41,"Nyasaye wefu Omulesi, ndeshela, nende abebusi banje babili, nende Abasuubili inyanga yokhubalwa ebikhole shingala iliula.""
  14,42,"Ne olaparakhwo mbu Nyasaye akandalanga khuka abamabii bakholanga tawe. Toto ye abasitinjia imbeli okhula Inyanga yetsimoni tsilikhookha."